    <patterns>
      <pattern name="Regression test shape" location="src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/components/conversation/__tests__/natural-language.regression.test.ts (new)">
        For each natural-language input: parse → assert `command: null` + `references: []`. Then mock BFF payload + assert `commandIntent` is null/absent. Then mock CapabilityRouter response + assert behavior matches pre-Pillar-8 baseline.
      </pattern>
